3/10/taylor-swift-jack-antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/taylor-swift-jack-antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/taylor-swift-jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/taylor-swift-jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>分享了一篇感谢她的朋友兼合作者杰克·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff)</a>的帖子，并透露他们的歌曲“比小说更甜”(Sweeter Than Fiction) 已接受“泰勒版”处理。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">泰勒·斯威夫特 - “1989（泰勒版）”评论：她最好的专辑永远不会过时</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（10月29日），斯威夫特在社交媒体上称赞安东诺夫，称这首歌是他们一起写的第一首歌。 “你会站在那里十英尺高，我会说‘我一直都知道’。这首歌总是让我想起我的朋友杰克。这是我们一起创作的第一首歌，多年来看着他挑战自我并创造出美丽的艺术，这是我一生中最激动的事情。”她写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cy_ffVourVt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><